111/* Return true if the LHS of a call should be removed. */
112
113inline bool
114should_remove_lhs_p (tree lhs)
115{
116 return (lhs
117 && TREE_CODE (TYPE_SIZE_UNIT (TREE_TYPE (lhs))) == INTEGER_CST
118 && !TREE_ADDRESSABLE (TREE_TYPE (lhs)));
119}
